  "text": "The parametric study was conducted for the fixed-base conditions to determine the adequate number of integration points for the analysis. After examining the structural periods, wall base shear and storey shears, overturning moments and roof displacements, three integration points per element were selected as a rational compromise offering adequate accuracy, convergence and reasonable computational time. This is in line with the practice reported in the literature [CITATION_1] .",
